The following link contains information on featureCounts and how to run it locally through the GitHub bioinformatics notebook:
https://rnnh.github.io/bioinfo-notebook/docs/featureCounts.html

The following specific featureCounts settings were used for this specific Mcoln1 mouse model study:
Paired end reads?: true
Genome annotation: Mus_musculus.GRCm39.109.gtf
Mapped reads: (All 28 .bam files)
Threads: 4
Feature type: exon
Gene attribute: gene_id
